{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "溺火", "storyInfo": "城裡的愛布拉娜迎來了一位意料之外的客人，而城外的遺跡中，一場葬禮，同時也是塔拉傳統的還火儀式，正在拉芙希妮面前舉行。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g12_castlecorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "堡壘內的僕役已經全數被我遣退，那麼這腳步聲……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……殿下。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，是你啊。來找我有什麼事？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不問我為什麼還回得來嗎？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不問。你回來了，僅此而已，我忠心的僕臣。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，你能為我帶來一位什麼樣的客人，我心裡自然有數。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……宵禁開始了嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛開始。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這也不算違背了我的命令。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_652_1#6$1", "posfrom": "0,90", "posto": "0,90", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.6, "bstart": 0.5, "bend": 0.8, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.65", "scale": 1.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dullthunderclap"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……失敗……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失敗了？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "納斯爾紗仍在此處，我也仍在此處，談何失敗？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……逃離……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "期限是夏末節。就算黑霧以不聽人言聞名，這一點想必也還記得住。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……不出所料……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……令人失望……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……不可接受……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，我該如何理解你的隻言片語呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者……你也覺得話語的交流，不如法術與毀滅來得直接？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜話音未落，泛著冷光的枝葉就從黑霧中探出，直指她的咽喉。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireburst", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與此同時，她的槍也刺進了厚重的霧氣深處，紫色的火光在其中隱約可見，只等一個念頭就將霧氣燃盡。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但枝葉畢竟並未刺進愛布拉娜的咽喉，紫火也並未在黑霧中間燃起。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夏末節。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夏末節第二天的朝陽升起之前，我們都會得到那個結果。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於現在……我們都不過是在虛張聲勢罷了，不是嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜維持著刺入黑霧的姿勢，但頃刻之後，她咽喉前的枝葉憑空消失，她槍尖的火焰也隨之熄滅。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑霧隨即散去。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在這裡啊。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，還有事嗎？關於深池？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這裡只有你我，我最忠心的僕臣，我允許你再度提起這個詞。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的寬宏，但是，不。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫助一個國家建立的鬼魂也仍然是鬼魂，鬼魂不應該被銘刻在歷史上。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我的確擔憂那天和我一樣留在原地的幾位同僚……他們如今在何處？他們是否會對您不利？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無需擔心。而且，這應當不是你冒著風險一直留到現在的原因。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在回來的路上，我看見了一片混亂。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人越來越狂躁，為了一點東西……甚至不為了什麼就大打出手，而另一些人卻像木偶般僵在原地……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿他們都是……當年隨我們一同對抗維多利亞人的鬼魂。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們也會沒入黑暗嗎？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡畢竟是納斯爾紗，紅龍的巢穴，塔拉的首府。我怕這裡發生的一切都將震動整個塔拉。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來仍不信服。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下……我……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歸根究柢，我只有一個問題。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有這個問題，我懇請您給我一個答覆。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我准許你的僭越。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深吸氣）", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛布拉娜殿下，那個未來……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個您曾向深池許諾，向所有塔拉人許諾的未來，那個塔拉人能自由書寫自己的夢想的未來……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是假的嗎？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "校官的全身不住顫抖，連日來潛藏在心底的恐懼在一瞬間攫住了他。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那恐懼和自己的下場無關。他不怕像同僚那樣被黑霧吞沒，不怕自己因為觸怒紅龍而死。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只怕從紅龍口中聽見那個自己從來不敢設想的答案。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕無虛假。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經回答你了，校官。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#5$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍的聲音飄渺、虛弱，卻不容置疑。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽著這無數次指揮自己走向勝利的聲音，男人的脊背緩緩挺直。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信您。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者……你只是沒有相信以外的選擇？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我相信您，相信您如同此前無數次一樣，選擇令人費解，甚至看起來走不通的道路，但總能將我們帶到離那個理想更近的地方。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的信任倒的確值得我的一聲感謝了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，納斯爾紗城內的秩序並不需要你去維護。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你能從黑林中歸來，那麼你此刻就應當回到黑林中去。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到夏末節過去？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#13$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“清晨我走入黑林，呼喚迷霧”……", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下？", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽見那黑林外傳來的歌聲了嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#16$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離你出城，也就不過一次日出日落的時間……做得不錯，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#9$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城內竟然發生了這樣的事？！", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，你姐姐……她究竟在謀劃什麼？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾有人向我保證，她的謀劃對塔拉有益而無害。然而無論是她，還是幫她作證的人，此刻我都無法相信。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守靈人，已經到這份上了，你們都不幫葦草一把嗎？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她為了葬禮而來，我們也只為此才接納她。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我已知曉逝者的生平了。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿著這些繩結和花環，我們到外面去，葬禮就要開始了。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們收起分歧，默默站起。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g6_remains_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "清晨我走入黑林，呼喚迷霧♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "踏上通往戰場的路途♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "沒有笛聲，沒有戰鼓♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "唯有身後鐘聲，穿過霧中的水珠♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的守靈人都低聲唱著歌，手頭做著不同的事情。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們中有的人在裝點逝者的遺體——但那也僅僅是往木匣上擺放繩結和花環罷了。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人在木匣周圍架起柴草。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人則一邊唱著，一邊往前來參加葬禮的流民們手中分發蠟燭。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小小的，明亮的火光在營地各處搖曳。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮也分到一盞，她小心地將其捧在胸前。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請說。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不認識逝者，說實話也沒什麼重要的事情要說……但是，在我故鄉的葬禮上，大家都可以隨便說話的。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這本就是塔拉人尊敬逝者的方式。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便已經結束，生命仍然值得慶祝，更不用說生者的歡欣對死者而言即是告慰。請隨意交談。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還做了一些點心……", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也請自由分享。稍後我們也會有飲食提供給各位。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，考慮到庫林先生英年早逝，又因城內變故橫死，一些過度的行為還請各位克制。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，在還火的過程中，請各位聽我們的安排。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭，你們那邊的葬禮是這樣舉辦的嗎？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說就只是停靈守夜而已，並沒有這麼多傳統的步驟，我也不知道“還火”究竟是什麼。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正等一下聽人家的就是了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，你以前參加過這種儀式嗎？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎……", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g12_castlecorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說……", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉芙希妮已經與守靈人會合，英雄真正的葬禮開始了。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“清晨我走入黑林，呼喚迷霧，踏上通往戰場的路途”……這首歌你會唱嗎？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_450_necras_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您明知故問了。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有多少次，我都是唱著這首歌，帶著年輕人們走向戰場的。", "name": "校官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g14_galekingruins_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰？是誰在唱歌？", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，好不容易從黑林裡逃出來，都已經走到了舊王城的遺址，怎麼還是能聽見這首歌？", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我還沒走出黑林？！", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不對，是……遺跡中央的熔爐在發出聲音？", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多美的旋律啊……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有笛聲，沒有戰鼓……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_247", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有身後鐘聲……穿過霧中的水珠……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我該回去……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我想要的東西，只有現在才能看清……", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我真的有資格……從納斯爾紗逃走嗎？", "name": "“歌唱家”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_247"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾瑪，給你，這是今天的麵包。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你還願意分一口吃的給我。", "name": "擔憂的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前你不是也把吃的分給我嗎？就當作是報恩吧。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你一直盯著我手裡的麵包，到底……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）克制，克制……", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）她是艾瑪，她是之前曾經把麵包分給你的人，你得幫她，你得——", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深呼吸）艾瑪，我沒事。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是、只是想說，你都病多久了，一直下不了床，接下來的日子不好過啊。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“沒有笛聲，沒有戰鼓”……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼突然唱起這首歌了？", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處……好像有人在唱……", "name": "擔憂的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g6_remains_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在還火儀式開始之前，請死者的親友致辭。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草小姐？", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……只有一份悼詞，是涅梅絲寫好交給我，讓我在葬禮上唸的。這樣可以嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然可以，請。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1691_1#4$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“給庫林……”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……信？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“庫林，也許過不了多久，我就會遭遇和你同樣的下場……”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g2_citystreets_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 100.0, "duration": 45.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "庫林，也許過不了多久，我就會遭遇和你同樣的下場。變成紫色火焰的傀儡，然後化為灰燼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或者，沒有人幫我解脫，我只能在死後無休止地煎熬下去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但我一直記得你以前和我說過的話。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你說，你想當這個英雄。讓你來當這個英雄吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你說，戰爭過後，納斯爾紗需要一個既不是深池也不是軍人，只屬於我們自己的英雄。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你說幾乎每一個納斯爾紗的人都在戰爭中失去了許多重要的東西，也許是戀人，也許是子女，也許是未來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果沒有一個英雄，沒有一個能理解他們，能為他們爭取權利，同時又能糾正他們、告誡他們的榜樣……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在戰爭結束，人們失去可以憎恨的對象的時候，他們會崩潰的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我覺得你說得對，我同意了你的要求。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "於是，你收養了提奧，你幫失去產業的人們謀生計，你……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你覺得一切都走在正確的路上，於是你提出了雕像的方案，你忘乎所以，自己把重負套在了自己的脖子上。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你在最後清醒了過來，但是……太晚了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "現在輪到我，替你背上這已經增殖到一個人的身軀難以承受的重擔。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g6_remains_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“……現在輪到我，替你背上這已經增殖到一個人的身軀難以承受的重擔。”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“別了，或者很快再見，庫林。”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“願你我最終……”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“在溫暖的火中重逢。”", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "59_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 55.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與悼詞唸完幾乎同時，一簇火焰被投向木匣周圍的柴草，整個柴堆熊熊燃燒起來。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們按照守靈人的指示，在火堆旁圍成一圈。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請用自己的雙眼確認，死者已在火中得享安寧，不再徘徊人間。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，請將燭火擺在離火堆盡可能近的地方，也可以直接將蠟燭投入火中，把火還給死者。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果對死者有任何話想說，都請對著火焰大聲說出口。無論是生者的讚美還是斥責，那都是記憶，都是逝者旅途中的慰藉。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把火還給死者之後，請不要離開，共同在此為死者守靈，直到火焰熄滅。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……開始吧。", "name": "嚴肅的守靈人"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願你獲得安息，未曾謀面的……", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……騙子，還有英雄。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭彎下腰，將蠟燭放在火邊。火舌一瞬間就將蠟燭吞沒，幾乎撲上了她的手。"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，要不要離火近一點？", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果在場有任何一個人沒資格紀念庫林，那只能是我。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是救不了他的。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當他決定要當一名真正的英雄時，他就已經不容於紅龍的那座巢穴了，不是嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，把火還給他吧。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓塵歸塵，土歸土，讓死者帶著我們的回憶沉睡，生者還要繼續生活下去。", "name": "莫蘭"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還火……", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓死者帶著我們的回憶沉睡……讓生者……繼續生活下去？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g6_remains_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在拉芙希妮若有所思的時間裡，還過火的人們紛紛坐到離火堆更遠的地方，最終手持燭火的只剩她一個。"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沉默著上前，將手裡的燭火投入了熊熊燃燒的火堆之中。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死者已矣。"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些躊躇滿志的、忘乎所以的、如夢初醒的、聲嘶力竭的片段，此刻都在火中燃盡，化為逸散的煙霧，或是沉默的灰燼。"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}